1. Case Overview
For years, the Minecraft dinosaur adventure series known informally as Tankee’s Dinos Reborn existed only as a fragmented childhood memory. No clips, no screenshots, no episode list, no documentation, and no online discussion remained. The series appeared to be completely lost.

This investigation aimed to:

confirm the show’s existence

locate the full episodes

identify the mods used

document the dinosaurs and characters

reconstruct the world and assets

preserve the series for future viewers

