6. World Reconstruction
The world layout — including the barn, jeep area, lab, biomes, and adventure paths — matches a modded Minecraft world built using both JurassiCraft and F&A Revival.

This confirms the show was not animated or custom‑modeled; it was created entirely inside Minecraft using high‑quality mods.

